{"tid":1561431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[新口號] 交代新屋嶺 還手足自由","createTime":"2019-09-11T15:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T08:35:31.000Z","uid":315502,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cb6cd0f9adcb0e86c89a4bd05d990fd32370591f","tid":1561431,"uid":315502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:00:01.000Z","msg":"各位手足，義士<br />\n<br />\n在下覺得有需要高度關注一下新屋嶺嘅情況，特別係人權同極之嚴重嘅暴力，根本就係虐待被捕者，仲要有好多係無辜嘅，真係路過都畀人捉入去。<br />\n<br />\n過去呢個禮拜，實在有太多新屋嶺嘅恐怖消息，除咗出返嚟嘅手續同我哋講之外，而家裏面發生咩事，有冇死人真係冇人知，亦都冇可能fact check到，目前為止爆咗出嚟嘅只係冰山一角。<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家除咗嗌&ldquo;光復香港 時代革命&rdquo;，幫手嗌埋&ldquo;交代新屋嶺 還手足自由&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"20b3ffbf4881a77b9523ba7ec2f8dac004bb4630","tid":1561431,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:00:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qftu6C0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqftu6C0.jpg&h=23ce3992&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cvOSjYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcvOSjYn.jpg&h=c1edffca&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"